quran[83]{c,v,t}:
  36,1,Ya’ seen
  36,2,NgeQur’an enobuhlakani
  36,3,Ngempela wena ungomunye wezithunywa
  36,4,Endleleni eqondile
  36,5,Isambulo sophakeme ngamandla onesihawu
  36,6,Ukuze wexwayise abantu ababengaxwayiswanga oyise ngakho- ke bona abanakile
  36,7,Ngempela izwi laqiniseka kwabaningi babo kepha bona bakholwa
  36,8,Ngempela thina sibeke amaketango ezintanyeni zabo afinyelela ezilevini ukuze amakhanda abo abheke phezulu
  36,9,Futhi sibeke okuvimbelayo ngaphambi kwabo nokumvimbelayo ngemva kwabo sabe sesiyabamboza ukuze bangaboni
  36,10,"Futhi\tkuyefana\tkubona\tnoma\tuyabaxwayisa\tnoma awubaxwayisi angeke bakholwe"
  36,11,"Kuphela ungakwazi ukuxwayisa lowo olandela isikhumbuzo futhi owesaba onomusa ongabonwayo, ngakho-ke mnike izindaba ezimnandi ngentethelelo nangomvuzo osezingeni eliphezulu"
  36,12,"Ngempela\tthina\tsiyabaphilisa\tabafile\rfuthi\rsikubhala phansi lokho abakubeke ngaphambili\rkanye\r(nalokho) okusezinyathelweni\tzabo\tfuthi\tzonke\rizinto\rsizibhalile emholini ocacile"
  36,13,Futhi benzele isibonelo sabantu bedolobha ngenkathi kufika kulona izithunywa
  36,14,Ngenkathi sithumela kubona (izithunywa) ezimbili base beyaziphika zombili sabe sesiyabaqinisa ngowesithathu basebethi “ngempela thina sithunyiwe kunina
  36,15,Bathi (abantu bedolobha) “nina aniyilutho ngaphandle kokuba ngabantu abafana nathi futhi onomusa akazange ambule lutho kuphela nina niqamba amanga”
  36,16,Zathi (izithunywa) “Inkosi yethu iyazi ukuthi thina siyizithunywa kunina”
  36,17,Futhi alikho icala kuthina ngaphandle kokudlulisela umyalezo ocacile
  36,18,"Bathi, “ngempela thina sibona ukubikezela okubi kunina uma ningaphezi ngempela sizonikhanda ngamatshe futhi nizothintwa yisijeziso esibuhlungu esivela kuthina”"
  36,19,"Zathi (izithunywa), “ukubikezela kwenu kukanye nani ngoba nikhunjuzisiwe kepha nina ningabantu abephula umthetho”"
  36,20,Futhi kwafika indoda ivela engxenyeni ebuqamama yedolobha igijima yathi “Oh Bantu bami! landelani izithunywa”
  36,21,Landelani labo abangawuceli umvuzo kunina futhi bona bangabaholelwe endleleni elungileyo
  36,22,Futhi kungani ukuthi ngingamkhonzi lowo owangidalayo futhi niyobubuyiselwa kuyena
  36,23,"Ngakube ngingazithathela omunye uNkulunkulu wamanga esikhundleni sakhe kulapho onomusa ehlose inhlupheko kumina na?, angeke kungisize ngalutho ukungincengela kwabo futhi angeke bangisindise"
  36,24,Ngempela mina ngiyobe ngisekudukeni okucacile
  36,25,Ngempela mina ngikholiwe eNkosini yenu ngakho-ke ngilaleleni
  36,26,"Kwathiwa, “ngena esivandeni (ezulwini)” wathi, “ngifisa sengathi abantu bami bangazi”"
  36,27,Ngokuthi iNkosi yami ingithethelele futhi yangibeka kanye nabahloniphekileyo
  36,28,Futhi asiyehliselanga phezulu kwabantu bakhe emva kwakhe impi evela ezulwini futhi kwakungadingeki ukuthi siyithumele
  36,29,Kwakungeyilutho kepha kwakungumsindo owodwa masinyane babethule du
  36,30,Oh ukuzisola ebantwini! Kwakungakaze kufike kubona isithunywa ngaphandle kokuthi babesenza inhlekisa
  36,31,Ngakube ababoni yini ukuthi zingaki izizukulwane esazibhubhisa ngaphambilini kwabo zona angeke zibuyele kubona
  36,32,Futhi ngempela bonke-bonke bayolethwa ngaphambili kwethu
  36,33,Futhi uphawu lwabo umhlaba ofile sawuphilisa sabe sesiveza kuwona uhlamvu kuze badle kulona
  36,34,Futhi kuwona sazenza izivande zamasundu nezamagilebhisi futhi kuwona sayenza imithombo ukuthi iqhume
  36,35,Ukuze badle ezithelweni zawo futhi izandla zabo azizitshalanga (izithelo) ngakube ababongi yini na
  36,36,Udumo malube kulowo owadala kwaba ngakubili kukona konke okuvezwa umhlaba kanye nokohlobo lwabo nakulokho abangakwazi
  36,37,"Futhi uphawu lwabo ubusuku, siyalukhipha usuku kubona kulapho bona besebumnyameni"
  36,38,"Futhi ilanga lihamba njalo liya lapho liphelela khona, lokho kungempoqo yophakeme ngamandla oyisazi"
  36,39,Nenyanga siyinqumele izimo ezibonakalayo kuze kube yilapho iphenduka iba njengegatsha lesundu elidala elomile
  36,40,Akusikhona okwelanga ukuthi lifice inyanga noma ubusuku ukuthi budlule imini futhi konke kuhamba emkhondweni
  36,41,Futhi uphawu lwabo ukuthi sayithwala inzalo yabo emkhunjini othweleyo
  36,42,"Futhi sibadalele okufana nako, lokhu abakugibelayo"
  36,43,Futhi uma sithanda singabaminzisa ngakho-ke angeke balekelelwe futhi bona angeke bahlengwe
  36,44,Ngaphandle komusa ovela kuthina kanye nenjabulo yesikhashana
  36,45,Futhi uma kuthiwa kubona “qaphelani loko okungaphambili kwenu kanye nalokho okungemumva kwenu ukuze mhlawumbe nithole umusa”
  36,46,Futhi alifiki kubona ivesi emavesini eNkosi yabo ngaphandle kokuba bayalifulathela
  36,47,Futhi uma kuthiwa kubona “sebenzisani kulokho anabela kona uMveliqangi” labo abangakholwanga bathi kulabo abakholwayo “ngakube singodla lowo okungathi uma ethanda uMvelinqangi amondle?” Anikwiyilutho ngaphandle kokuba sephutheni eligqamile
  36,48,"Futhi bathi, “siyofika nini lesisithembiso uma kungukuthi nina niqinisile?”"
  36,49,Abalindele lutho ngaphandle kokukhala okukodwa okuyobathatha kulapho bona bephikisana
  36,50,Ngakho-ke angeke bakwazi ukwenza ifa noma ukubuyela ebantwini babo
  36,51,Futhi liyoshawa icilongo kulapho bona beyophuma emathuneni beshesha bebheke eNkosini yabo
  36,52,"Bayothi, “Oh usizi kuthina! Ngubani lowo osivuse endaweni yethu, lokhu kuyilokhu onomusa akwethembisa nezithunywa zakhuluma iqiniso”"
  36,53,Angeke kube yilutho ngaphandle kokukhala okukodwa kulapho bona bonke beyolethwa ngaphambili kwethu
  36,54,Ngakho-ke ngalolusuku umphefumulo angeke wenziwe okungenabo ubulungiswa ngalutho futhi angeke ninikwe umvuzo ngaphandle kwaloko enanikwenza
  36,55,Ngempela izihlali zesivande kulolosuku ziyobamatasatasa ngezinto eziyinjabulo
  36,56,"Bona kanye namakhosikazi abo bayoba semthunzini, bacambalale endaweni ephakeme"
  36,57,Okwabo lapho phakathi yizithelo futhi okwabo kuyoba yinoma ngabe yini abayicelayo
  36,58,Ukuthula! Izwi elivela eNkosini enesihawu
  36,59,Futhi hlukanani namuhla Oh nina eniyizoni
  36,60,Angizange yini nginiphoqe Oh bantwana ba-Adam! Ukuthi ningamkhonzi usathane? Ngempela yena uyisitha senu esigqamile
  36,61,Nokuthi nikhonze mina? Lena yindlela elungile
  36,62,Futhi ngempela wadukisa iqembu elikhulu phakathi kwenu ngakube naningenawo yini umqondo
  36,63,Lesi yisihogo enanethenjiswe sona
  36,64,Ngenani kusona namhlanje ngenxa yokuthi naningakholwa
  36,65,Kulolusuku siyayisicilela imilomo yabo futhi izandla zabo zizokhuluma nezinyawo zabo zizofakaza mayelana naloko ababekusebenzela
  36,66,Futhi ukube besithanda besizosusa amehlo abo bese beyaphuphutheka endleleni bese bebona kanjani
  36,67,Futhi ukube besithanda besizobaguqula ezindaweni zabo bebengeke besakwazi ukuya phambili nokuphindela emumva
  36,68,"Futhi noma ngabe ngubani esimnika impilo ende simhlehlisela emumva endalweni, ngakube abanawo yini umqondo na"
  36,69,"Futhi asimfundisanga ubumbongi futhi akumfanele, yona ayiyilutho ngaphandle kwesikhumbuzo neQur’an ecacile"
  36,70,Ukuze ixwayise noma ngabe ngubani ophilayo futhi kuqiniseke izwi ukubhekana nabangakholwa
  36,71,Ababoni yini ukuthi sabadalela kuloko okwenziwe yizandla zethu izinkomo abangabanini bazo na
  36,72,Futhi sabathobisela zona ngakho-ke ezinye phakathi kwazo bayazigibela futhi ezinye phakathi kwazo bayazidla
  36,73,"Futhi banenzuzo kuzona kanye neziphuzo, ngakube ababongi yini na"
  36,74,Futhi esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi bazithathela izithixo ukuze mhlawumbe bathole usizo
  36,75,Azikwazi ukubasiza futhi bona kuzona bayibutho elilethwe ngaphambili
  36,76,Ngakho-ke ayingakuphathi kabi inkulumo yabo ngempela thina siyakwazi lokho abakufihlayo kanye nalokho abakuveza obala
  36,77,Ngakube umuntu akaboni yini ukuthi samdala ngeconsi lesidoda kulapho yena eyisitha esigqamile
  36,78,"Futhi wasenzela isibonelo wakhohlwa yindalo yakhe wathi, “ngubani onika amathambo impilo uma esewuthuli na?”"
  36,79,"Ithi, “uwanika impilo lowo owadalayo ngesikhathi sokuqala futhi yena uyisazi sazona zonke izidalwa”"
  36,80,Lowo owanibekela umlilo esihlahleni esiluhlaza kulapho nina nokhela kuwona
  36,81,Angeke yini lowo owadala amazulu nomhlaba akwazi ukudala okufana nabo na? Yebo! Yena ungumdali owaziyo
  36,82,"Kuphela, impoqo yakhe, uma ehlose into ethize uthi kuyona “yenzeka” bese iyenzeka"
  36,83,Ngakho-ke udumo malube kulowo esandleni sakhe ekunombuso wezinto zonke futhi niyophindiselwa kuyena